      "updated": 1770000000010,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Claude CLI path\n\nclaude-code factory\n  -> ClaudeCodeHandler\n  -> runClaudeCode()\n  -> RuntimeShimWrapper\n  -> claude -p --output-format stream-json\n  -> ClaudeCodeStreamTranslator\n  -> ApiStream chunks\n\nExecution is wrapped.\nOutput is structured JSON stream.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Claude CLI path\n\nclaude-code factory\n  -> ClaudeCodeHandler\n  -> runClaudeCode()\n  -> RuntimeShimWrapper\n  -> claude -p --output-format stream-json\n  -> ClaudeCodeStreamTranslator\n  -> ApiStream chunks\n\nExecution is wrapped.\nOutput is structured JSON stream.",
      "lineHeight": 1.24
    },
