      "updated": 1770000000012,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Kiro CLI path\n\nkiro-cli factory\n  -> KiroCliHandler\n  -> runKiroCli()\n  -> RuntimeShimWrapper\n  -> kiro-cli chat --no-interactive\n  -> plain line translator\n  -> ApiStream text chunks\n\nExecution is wrapped.\nOutput is plain text, so normalizer work remains.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Kiro CLI path\n\nkiro-cli factory\n  -> KiroCliHandler\n  -> runKiroCli()\n  -> RuntimeShimWrapper\n  -> kiro-cli chat --no-interactive\n  -> plain line translator\n  -> ApiStream text chunks\n\nExecution is wrapped.\nOutput is plain text, so normalizer work remains.",
      "lineHeight": 1.24
    },
